   "source": [
    "# 5.1 Mini-Batch Learning"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "5dbc90d3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Mini-Batch Learning (Important for DL)\n",
    "✅ What is it?\n",
    "\n",
    "Training on small subsets (batches) instead of full data or single data points.\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 Most commonly used in Deep Learning\n",
    "\n",
    "💻 Mini-Batch Code Example (DL)\n",
    "from tensorflow.keras.models import Sequential\n",
    "from tensorflow.keras.layers import Dense\n",
    "\n",
    "model = Sequential([\n",
    "    Dense(10, activation='relu', input_shape=(1,)),\n",
    "    Dense(1)\n",
    "])\n",
    "\n",
    "model.compile(optimizer='adam', loss='mse')\n",
    "\n",
    "X = [1,2,3,4,5,6]\n",
    "y = [2,4,6,8,10,12]\n",
    "\n",
    "# batch_size controls mini-batch\n",
    "model.fit(X, y, epochs=10, batch_size=2)\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 batch_size=2 → model trains in chunks\n",
    "\n",
    "🎯 When to Use What?\n",
    "✅ Use Batch Learning\n",
    "Historical data\n",
    "Offline training\n",
    "Example: Sales prediction\n",
    "✅ Use Online Learning\n",
    "Real-time systems\n",
    "Streaming data\n",
    "Example: Fraud detection\n",
    "✅ Use Mini-Batch Learning\n",
    "Deep Learning models\n",
    "Large datasets\n",
    "Example: Image recognition\n",
    "🧠 Simple Analogy\n",
    "Batch → Study entire book at once\n",
    "Online → Learn sentence by sentence\n",
    "Mini-batch → Learn chapter by chapter\n",
    "🎯 Interview-Ready Answer\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 “Batch learning trains models on the entire dataset at once, online learning updates the model incrementally with streaming data, and mini-batch learning strikes a balance by training on small subsets of data, which is widely used in deep learning for efficiency and stability.”\n",
    "\n",
    "🚀 Pro Insight (Very Important for YOU)\n",
    "\n",
    "For Data Scientist / GenAI roles:\n",
    "\n",
    "Batch → Most production pipelines\n",
    "Online → Real-time AI systems (high value skill)\n",
    "Mini-batch → Core of deep learning & LLM training"
   ]
  },
